<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Verify Your Email - Trove</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #fff1f1;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      }

      table {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 0;
        background-color: #fff1f1;
      }

      .email-container {
        width: 600px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        overflow: hidden;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 32px 0 16px;
      }

      .logo img {
        max-width: 180px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #ffe5e5;
        padding: 36px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: #db4444;
        font-size: 32px;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .image-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .image-section img {
        max-width: 360px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .body-content {
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .body-content p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #541212;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .body-content strong {
        color: #db4444;
      }

      .cta-button {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }

      .cta-button a {
        background-color: #db4444;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: inline-block;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button a:hover {
        background-color: #bf2e2e;
      }

      .steps-title {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #7f1f1f;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .steps ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #b91c1c;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .expiry-note {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #a42525;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #ffecec;
        padding: 20px 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #a82e2e;
        margin: 4px 0;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #db4444;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <table cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'>
      <tr>
        <td align='center'>
          <div class='logo'>
            <img
              src='{{clientUrl}}/assets/images/logo-horizontal.png'
              alt='Trove'
            />
          </div>

          <table class='email-container' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'>
            <tr>
              <td class='header'>
                <h1>üéâ One Last Step ‚Äî Let&apos;s Get You Started!</h1>
                <p style='margin-top: 12px; font-size: 16px; color: #7a1212'>
                  Verify your email to unlock everything
                  <strong>Trove</strong>
                  has to offer.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class='image-section'>
                <img
                  src='{{clientUrl}}/assets/images/verify-email.png'
                  alt='Verify Your Email'
                />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class='body-content'>
                <p>Hey there üëã</p>

                <p>
                  Thanks for joining
                  <strong>Trove</strong>
                  ‚Äî we&apos;re thrilled to have you! Please verify your email
                  address to finish setting up your account.
                </p>

                <div class='cta-button'>
                  <a href='{{link}}'>Verify My Email</a>
                </div>

                <p class='steps-title'>What happens next?</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>You&apos;ll land on a secure verification page</li>
                  <li>Click the button to confirm your email</li>
                  <li>
                    You&apos;re in ‚Äî your Trove account will be ready to use
                  </li>
                </ul>

                <p class='expiry-note'>
                  ‚ö†Ô∏è This link will expire in
                  <strong>10 minutes</strong>
                  to keep your account secure.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class='footer'>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Trove. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>
                  Need help?
                  <a href='mailto:{{supportEmail}}'>{{supportEmail}}</a>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>